{
  "chapter": 31,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十一回「死亡之吻」摘要：楚留香与水母阴姬在水底激战，楚留香利用呼吸优势消耗阴姬内力，最终将其制服。宫南燕趁机启动喷泉将二人冲出水面，楚留香为阻止阴姬呼吸而以嘴封住其口，形成「死亡之吻」。阴姬流泪求饶，楚留香心软放手，却被宫南燕点穴擒获。阴姬醒来后击败宫南燕，揭露宫南燕杀害雄娘子的秘密，并因楚留香的仁慈而释放众人。阴姬最终选择自我封闭，楚留香与胡铁花等人会合离开神水宫。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我早就说过，从没有人能在神水宫占得了便宜的，就连战无不胜的楚留香也不能例外。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "现在，你已承认自己战败了么?",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "看来我已非承认不可。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你还有什么话说?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "我已没有什么话好说了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "你说，我们应该如何处置他?",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "这人被你所俘，应该由你作主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "也好，就将他交给我吧!",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "你是不是也想像对付雄娘子那样对付他?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "这是他告诉你的?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "你是不是没有想到他会看到你的秘密?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，是我杀了那个人，我若杀错了，替他偿命也无妨，但偷看别人秘密的人，也得死。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "你……你?",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "你怎么……怎么忍心对我下手?",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "你怎么忍心对他下手?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "他?谁?是楚留香?还是雄娘子?",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "原来你还是爱他?原来我只不过是他的代用品，你竟不惜杀了我替他报仇，但你可知道我杀他是为了你么?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "那么你为什么还要……还要……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "你不杀他，我也许会杀他，但你杀了他，我就要为他报仇，无论谁杀了他，我都要为他报仇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "你的意思，我已经懂了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "你懂了最好，我也希望你能懂。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "但你莫忘了，若不是我，你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "我也知道你救了我，但那是另外一回事，我会好好安葬你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "我现在才真的明白你是为了什么杀我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "你杀我，只因我救了你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "我死了之后，就永远没有人知道你曾经败在楚留香手上，也不会有人知道我曾经救过你，你从来不能忍受失败的耻辱，所以非杀我不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "你一向都很聪明，也许太聪明了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我究竟是聪明还是笨，连我自己都不知道。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你认为我真的是为了她救了我才杀她的么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "我想你并不是这种人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她了解我难道还没有你清楚?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "那只因她自己是这种人，所以才会将你看得和她一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，就因为你并不是这种人，才会说我也不是，你若非这种人，她也许就根本没有机会救我了。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你可知道你这次为何会失败么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "我知不知道又有何分别?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你应该知道的，你这次失败，只因为你的心太软了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "你呢?你的心难道从来不软?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我的心?你以为我还有心?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "就因为我已什么都没有了，所以，你的生死对我也已无关紧要，我甚至已懒得杀你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "你……你难道已经想……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我怎么想，也与你无关，你快走，莫等我改变了主意。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阴姬",
      "listener": "char_di_zi",
      "text": "带这人去找你三师姐，叫她将另外的三个人也全都放了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "多谢宫主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我们走吧!",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "老臭虫，你怎么跑出来的?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你们怎么跑出来的?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "还是你先说吧，你遇着的事一定比我们精彩，我们的故事实在有点泄气。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "还是你先说吧，我这故事说来话长。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "说来真丢人，我们三个人竟全不是水母的对手，若不是蓉儿的姑妈，我们只怕已见不着你了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "她放了你们?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，她和一个叫'九妹'的一起来盘问我们，我们自然什么也不肯说，但那叫'九妹'的小丫头倒真凶得很，居然要用苦刑来糟蹋我们，幸好蓉儿姑妈说我们都是有身份的人，应该以礼相待，谁知那小丫头翻了脸，硬说蓉儿的姑妈一定早已和我们串通了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那小丫头人凶嘴也凶，还说了许多很难听的话，蓉儿的姑妈忍无可忍，忽然间出手点了她的穴道。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "她……她怎能如此冒险?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    }
  ],
